title: Better and better
text: Outlook is getting better and better, I’ve multiple accounts: personal hotmail, two different biz email accounts, they all work under one outlook app; just great!

title: Much better than built in mail app for iPhone
text:
The basic built in mail app for iPhone is fine, but does not have many features. This mobile app for Outlook has many more of the full desktop mail features. 
Personally I find outlook to be much more logical and user friendly than gmail. I’m not a gmail fan in general.

title: I like this app for Outlook or Live Emails!
text: This app is just like being on a desktop or a laptop computer, with current updates and real time! And, it is easy to email with this app send, with this app you could also speak into the phone and the email will automatically type the email making it easier to use!
